Description: # flask-handlers
        
        ## How to install?
        ```bash
        $ pip install flask_handlers
        ```
        
        ## How to use?
        ```python
        from flask import Flask
        from flask_handlers import set_json_error_handler
        
        app = Flask(__name__)
        set_json_error_handler(app)
        ```
        
